      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SWEET TILLY (8) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (20.10) at this track behind Coolhand Sue in a Maiden. Led around the bend before fighting on well and should give a sight. Makes plenty of appeal. SUNSET BOY (3) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 352m behind Divine Suzanne (20.44) in a Maiden. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Cannot be left out. POPPY DAY (5) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a one length second (20.01) behind Divine Suzanne at this track. Expected to feature again. MISS MULGOWIE (1) can fill a top-three spot.",
